File:Corvus brachyrhynchos 30196.JPG|The American [[crow]] is one of the most intelligent of all animals.<ref name="pbs">{{cite web|url=http://video.pbs.org/video/1621910826/#|title=A Murder of Crows|date=2010-10-24|work=Nature|publisher=PBS video|accessdate=6 February 2011|quote=''New research indicates that crows are among the brightest animals in the world.''}}</ref>
