File:Die Uniformen der Allgemeinen SS 32-45.jpg|Black uniform of an SS officer (1932–45). The [[SS]] was the military wing of the [[Nazi Party]].
File:ShababFlag.svg|Flag of [[Ansar al-Sharia (Yemen)|Ansar al-Sharia]] Islamic movement in [[Yemen]]. Variations of the [[Black Standard]] are used by [[Islamists]] and [[Jihadists]] across the [[Muslim]] world.
</gallery>

